 heavyweight fleece. Structured 3-panel hood. Concealed interior zippers.\"/><meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://kvrn.com\"/><meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"KVRN\"/><meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GB\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"KVRN — Heavyweight Oversized Hoodies &amp; Sweatpants\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"400 GSM+ heavyweight fleece. Quiet luxury.\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\"/><link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/apple-touch-icon.png\"/><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"ClothingStore\",\"name\":\"KVRN\",\"url\":\"https://kvrn.com\",\"description\":\"Quiet luxury meets premium utility. Heavyweight oversized hoodies and sweatpants.\",\"sameAs\":[\"https://instagram.com/kvrn\",\"https://tiktok.com/@kvrn\"]}</script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"bg-kvrn-bg text-kvrn-text font-body antialiased\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><a href=\"#main-content\" class=\"skip-link\">Skip to main content</a><script>\n          window.dataLayer=window.dataLayer||[];\n          function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}\n          gtag('consent','default',{analytics_storage:'denied',ad_storage:'denied',functionality_storage:'granted',wait_for_update:500});\n        </script><header class=\"fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-[200] h-[56px] flex items-center transition-all duration-300 bg-[var(--color-bg)] text-[var(--color-text)]\" aria-label=\"Site header\"><div class=\"kvrn-container w-full flex items-center justify-between\"><a class=\"text-[13px] font-light tracking-[0.2em] uppercase hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity duration-150\" aria-label=\"KVRN — go to homepage\" href=\"/\">KVRN</a><nav class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-10\" aria-label=\"Primary navigation\"><a class=\"text-[11px] font-light tracking-[0.14em] uppercase hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity duration-150\" href=\"/shop\">Shop</a><a class=\"text-[11px] font-light tracking-[0.14em] uppercase hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity duration-150\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"text-[11px] font-light tracking-[0.14em] uppercase hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity duration-150\" href=\"/waitlist\">Waitlist</a></nav><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6\"><button class=\"text-[11px] font-light tracking-[0.14em] uppercase hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity duration-150\" aria-label=\"Shopping bag\">Bag</button><button class=\"md:hidden flex flex-col gap-[5px] p-1 -mr-1\" aria-label=\"Open menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"mobile-nav\"><span class=\"block h-px w-[22px] transition-colors duration-300\" style=\"background-color:var(--color-text)\"></span><span class=\"block h-px w-[22px] transition-colors duration-300\" style=\"background-color:var(--color-text)\"></span></button></div></div></header><div class=\"fixed inset-0 z-[300] bg-black/40 transition-opacity duration-300 md:hidden opacity-0 pointer-events-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div id=\"mobile-nav\" role=\"dialog\" aria-modal=\"true\" aria-label=\"Navigation menu\" class=\"fixed inset-y-0 left-0 z-[400] w-[min(340px,100vw)] bg-[var(--color-bg)] flex flex-col px-6 pt-7 pb-10 overflow-y-auto transition-transform duration-500 ease-[cubic-bezier(0.25,0.46,0.45,0.94)] md:hidden -translate-x-full\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-10 flex-shrink-0\"><a class=\"text-[13px] font-light tracking-[0.2em] uppercase\" href=\"/\">KVRN</a><button class=\"p-2 -mr-2 text-[var(--color-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors\" aria-label=\"Close menu\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 3L15 15M15 3L3 15\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></button></div><nav class=\"flex-1 space-y-8\" aria-label=\"Mobile navigation\"><div><p class=\"kvrn-label text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-3\">Shop</p><div class=\"space-y-1\"><a class=\"block py-2.5 text-[15px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] hover:text-[var(--color-muted)] transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/shop\">All Products</a><a class=\"block py-2.5 text-[15px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] hover:text-[var(--color-muted)] transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/products/kvrn-heavyweight-hoodie\">Heavyweight Hoodie</a><a class=\"block py-2.5 text-[15px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] hover:text-[var(--color-muted)] transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/products/kvrn-heavyweight-sweatpants\">Heavyweight Sweatpants</a></div></div><div><p class=\"kvrn-label text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-3\">Brand</p><div class=\"space-y-1\"><a class=\"block py-2.5 text-[15px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] hover:text-[var(--color-muted)] transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/about\">About KVRN</a><a class=\"block py-2.5 text-[15px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] hover:text-[var(--color-muted)] transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/waitlist\">Waitlist</a></div></div><div><p class=\"kvrn-label text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-3\">Support</p><div class=\"space-y-1\"><a class=\"block py-2.5 text-[15px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] hover:text-[var(--color-muted)] transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/support/faq\">FAQ</a><a class=\"block py-2.5 text-[15px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] hover:text-[var(--color-muted)] transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/support/shipping-returns\">Shipping &amp; Returns</a><a class=\"block py-2.5 text-[15px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] hover:text-[var(--color-muted)] transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/support/size-guide\">Size Guide</a><a class=\"block py-2.5 text-[15px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] hover:text-[var(--color-muted)] transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></div></div></nav><div class=\"mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-[var(--color-border)] flex gap-5 flex-shrink-0\"><a href=\"https://instagram.com/kvrn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-[11px] tracking-[0.14em] uppercase text-[var(--color-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors\">Instagram</a></div></div><div class=\"fixed inset-0 z-[300] transition-all duration-300 bg-transparent pointer-events-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div role=\"dialog\" aria-modal=\"true\" aria-label=\"Shopping bag\" class=\"fixed top-0 right-0 bottom-0 z-[400] w-full max-w-[400px] bg-[var(--color-bg)] flex flex-col transition-transform duration-[550ms] ease-[cubic-bezier(0.25,0.46,0.45,0.94)] translate-x-full\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-5 border-b border-[var(--color-border)]\"><h2 class=\"text-[11px] font-light tracking-[0.14em] uppercase\">Bag</h2><button aria-label=\"Close bag\" class=\"p-2 -mr-2 opacity-40 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 3l12 12M15 3L3 15\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto scrollbar-thin\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center h-full px-6 text-center gap-5\"><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">Your bag is empty.</p><a href=\"/shop\"><button aria-busy=\"false\" class=\"relative inline-flex items-center justify-center font-body font-light tracking-widest uppercase transition-all duration-150 ease-out select-none whitespace-nowrap -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent bg-transparent text-kvrn-text border border-kvrn-text hover:bg-kvrn-text hover:text-kvrn-bg active:bg-[#333333] disabled:opacity-40 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:pointer-events-none h-10 px-5 text-[11px]\"><span class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">Browse collection</span></button></a></div></div></div><main id=\"main-content\"><div class=\"pt-[56px]\"><div class=\"container-kvrn section-padding max-w-2xl\"><nav aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\" class=\"mb-10\"><ol class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-[11px] text-kvrn-muted tracking-wide\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-kvrn-text transition-colors\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li aria-hidden=\"true\">·</li><li class=\"text-kvrn-text\" aria-current=\"page\">Privacy Policy</li></ol></nav><h1 class=\"font-display font-light text-[40px] md:text-[48px] leading-none tracking-tighter mb-3\">Privacy Policy</h1><p class=\"label-11 text-kvrn-muted mb-14\">Last updated: <!-- -->1 January 2025</p><div class=\"space-y-10 text-[14px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\"><section><h2 class=\"text-[15px] font-light text-kvrn-text mb-3\">Who we are</h2><p>KVRN is operated by [KVRN Ltd], a company registered in England and Wales (Company No. [XXXXXXXX]). Our registered address is [address]. We are the data controller for the personal information we collect about you.</p><p class=\"mt-3\">For questions about this policy, contact us at<!-- --> <a href=\"mailto:hello@kvrn.com\" class=\"text-kvrn-text underline underline-offset-2\">hello@kvrn.com</a>.</p></section><div class=\"rule\"></div><section><h2 class=\"text-[15px] font-light text-kvrn-text mb-3\">What data we collect and why</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"border-l-2 border-kvrn-border pl-4 space-y-1\"><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-kvrn-text\">Name, email address, shipping address</p><p>To process and fulfil your order.</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-kvrn-subtle\">Contract — processing is necessary to deliver what you ordered.</p></div><div class=\"border-l-2 border-kvrn-border pl-4 space-y-1\"><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-kvrn-text\">Payment details (card number, CVV)</p><p>To take payment.</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-kvrn-subtle\">Contract — processed and tokenised by Stripe. We never see or store your card number.</p></div><div class=\"border-l-2 border-kvrn-border pl-4 space-y-1\"><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-kvrn-text\">Phone number (optional)</p><p>To send shipping notifications or drop alerts by SMS, if you opt in.</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-kvrn-subtle\">Consent — you can opt out at any time by replying STOP.</p></div><div class=\"border-l-2 border-kvrn-border pl-4 space-y-1\"><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-kvrn-text\">Email address (waitlist)</p><p>To notify you when new drops go live.</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-kvrn-subtle\">Consent — you can unsubscribe at any time via any email we send.</p></div><div class=\"border-l-2 border-kvrn-border pl-4 space-y-1\"><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-kvrn-text\">IP address, device type, browser, pages visited</p><p>To understand how our site is used (via Google Analytics 4 and Microsoft Clarity).</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-kvrn-subtle\">Consent — only collected if you accept analytics cookies.</p></div><div class=\"border-l-2 border-kvrn-border pl-4 space-y-1\"><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-kvrn-text\">IP address (fraud signals)</p><p>To detect and prevent fraudulent orders.</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-kvrn-subtle\">Legitimate interest — protecting our business and genuine customers.</p></div></div></section><div class=\"rule\"></div><section><h2 class=\"text-[15px] font-light text-kvrn-text mb-3\">Who we share data with</h2><p class=\"mb-4\">We never sell your personal data. We share it only with the services required to operate:</p><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 font-light text-kvrn-text min-w-[160px]\">Stripe</span><span>Payment processing (PCI DSS Level 1 certified)</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 font-light text-kvrn-text min-w-[160px]\">Shipping partner</span><span>Shipping label generation and order tracking</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 font-light text-kvrn-text min-w-[160px]\">Email service</span><span>Transactional email delivery</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 font-light text-kvrn-text min-w-[160px]\">SMS service</span><span>SMS notifications (opt-in only)</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 font-light text-kvrn-text min-w-[160px]\">Neon</span><span>Database hosting (encrypted at rest)</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 font-light text-kvrn-text min-w-[160px]\">Cloudflare</span><span>Hosting, CDN, and security</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 font-light text-kvrn-text min-w-[160px]\">Google Analytics 4</span><span>Anonymous website analytics (consent-gated)</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 font-light text-kvrn-text min-w-[160px]\">Microsoft Clarity</span><span>Session recordings (consent-gated)</span></li></ul></section><div class=\"rule\"></div><section><h2 class=\"text-[15px] font-light text-kvrn-text mb-3\">How long we keep data</h2><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li>Order data: 7 years (required by HMRC for tax purposes)</li><li>Marketing preferences (email/SMS consent): Until you withdraw consent</li><li>Analytics data: 14 months (Google Analytics default)</li><li>Session recordings: 30 days (Microsoft Clarity default)</li></ul></section><div class=\"rule\"></div><section><h2 class=\"text-[15px] font-light text-kvrn-text mb-3\">Your rights</h2><p class=\"mb-4\">Under UK GDPR, you have the right to:</p><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-2 w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-kvrn-muted\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>Access the personal data we hold about you</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-2 w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-kvrn-muted\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>Correct inaccurate data</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-2 w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-kvrn-muted\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>Request erasure of your data (subject to legal retention obligations)</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-2 w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-kvrn-muted\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>Restrict or object to how we process your data</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-2 w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-kvrn-muted\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>Data portability — receive your data in a structured format</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-2 w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-kvrn-muted\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>Withdraw consent at any time (for consent-based processing)</li></ul><p class=\"mt-4\">To exercise any of these rights, email<!-- --> <a href=\"mailto:hello@kvrn.com\" class=\"text-kvrn-text underline underline-offset-2\">hello@kvrn.com</a>. We will respond within 30 days. If you are unhappy with our response, you may contact the ICO:<!-- --> <a href=\"https://ico.org.uk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-kvrn-text underline underline-offset-2\">ico.org.uk</a>.</p></section><div class=\"rule\"></div><section><h2 class=\"text-[15px] font-light text-kvrn-text mb-3\">Cookies</h2><p>We use essential cookies (required for the site to function) and optional analytics cookies (only with your consent). See our<!-- --> <a class=\"text-kvrn-text underline underline-offset-2\" href=\"/cookies\">Cookie Policy</a> <!-- -->for full details.</p></section><div class=\"rule\"></div><section><h2 class=\"text-[15px] font-light text-kvrn-text mb-3\">Changes to this policy</h2><p>We may update this policy. We will notify customers of material changes by email. The “Last updated” date at the top of this page reflects the most recent revision.</p></section></div></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"border-t border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-bg)]\" aria-label=\"Site footer\"><div class=\"kvrn-container\"><div class=\"py-16 md:py-24 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-[2f